{"tid":858675,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"林鄭：特區政府致力達至終極普選特首","createTime":"2018-10-12T03:34:25.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-12T06:00:07.000Z","uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":16,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"e7fb0e678cb3d5703f67a0a9d78ca9397038a82e","tid":858675,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-12T03:34:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://static.stheadline.com/stheadline/inewsmedia/20181009/_2018100910015919266.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.stheadline.com%2Fstheadline%2Finewsmedia%2F20181009%2F_2018100910015919266.jpg&h=fe826f96&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n特首林鄭月娥表示，《基本法》列明香港最終達至普選特首，政府會致力達至此目標，但這工作曾受挫敗，如果要重啟普選工作，政府要非常小心處理並考慮有無通過的機會，尤其工作涉及全國人大的決定。<br />\n<br />\n林鄭月娥今早出席港台英文台節目，解釋新一份施政報告，其間談到23條立法和政制議題。她提到社會經常比較《基本法》23條及45條，但顯然23條須本地立法，政府應在1997年後制定，但關於特首選舉的45條則是循序漸進實行。<br />\n<br />\n被問到建制派認為她在23條立法上的態度太軟弱，林鄭月娥表示，已學習到作為特首，處事太開明會有些政黨不高興，如果被指親內地又會被另一陣營攻擊，所以她只會為市民做正確的事。"},{"pid":"f0a3c22455ed3a5f4fafd6666fe83f0008ad85d6","tid":858675,"uid":20933,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-12T03:34:38.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://m.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20181012/s00001/1539311969351\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20181012%2Fs00001%2F1539311969351&d=z5r78ieZp71fnBT0IHEi3ZUJf0bKPU4tHf%2BJg0Yv85M%3D&h=4cd9f33a\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20181012%2Fs00001%2F1539311969351&h=3d9ba6b5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://m.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20181012/s00001/1539311969351</a>"},{"pid":"4fa0d1aaf3c09d5166a5f26724534a768afe2bdb","tid":858675,"uid":40763,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-12T03:50:12.000Z","msg":"美國殺到埋來啦？"},{"pid":"a97683ed3ee9ad9ab01d7fb92a8ec60994d436fa","tid":858675,"uid":26329,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0